{"tid":884040,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【流拍收場】環海．東岸拍賣單位 無人承價收回","createTime":"2018-10-31T09:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T14:15:45.000Z","uid":122377,"like":153,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"0b379ee4184da0c14e93a5c0460d22c50580eeff","tid":884040,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"有「劏房之城」的紅磡環海．東岸，未入伙先有業主將單位拍賣。黃開基拍賣行，今日推出環海．東岸1A座27樓L室拍賣，實用面積194方呎，開放式間隔，開價440萬元，呎價22,680元，開價僅較業主2015年10月購入價407萬元，高出33萬元或8%。<br />\n<br />\n拍賣行現場約7人到場，全程無人舉手叫價，最終流拍收場<br />\n<br />\n本月10日，黃開基拍賣行首度拍賣紅磡環海．東岸1C座29樓D室，實用230方呎，開放式間隔，開價528萬元，最終零承接，流拍告終。到場的女士表示，「環海東岸的價格未到心水價，睇定啲（樓市）」<br />\n<br />\n睇黎呢個盤 唔輸錢都好難走得甩<br />\n3年前買都搞成咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麥包RIP"},{"pid":"646f3c6d08e3930d780a35258ad26022b0377395","tid":884040,"uid":34251,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"唔計"},{"pid":"8a786345230f115b1d1956e66072cceabf7eea07","tid":884040,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"646f3c6d08e3930d780a35258ad26022b0377395","tid":884040,"uid":34251,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1ea2c2150f0db789067ddda78a2bd9cda0b80a","tid":884040,"uid":122377,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"其實好撚慘 <br />\n3年樓花 到今日都未收到樓 <br />\n想賣都賣唔到 要靠拍賣行<br />\n地產商又一撚狗傑作"},{"pid":"1e164a0fb3d7d75a3c61a0e3e7f0b4d18e86d86e","tid":884040,"uid":52010,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"拍賣行現場約7人到場，全程無人舉手叫價"},{"pid":"bd15a73d6